Sentivo — Market Sentiment & Pulse Engine

Data Flow:
Reddit ──> RedditProducer ──┐
                           ├── raw_text_data ──> SentimentConsumer
NewsAPI ─> NewsProducer   ──┘
yFinance > MarketDataProducer ──> raw_market_data
                                        │
                             analyzed_sentiment
                                        │
                          AggregatorConsumer ──> aggregated_metrics
                                                       │
                                            SignalConsumer ──> trade_signals
                                                                    │
                                                              LoggingSink
